channel.title: I'm leaving and I leave you a gift
channel.description:
Hello, I'm not used to posting things around here, I came to donate one of my projects which I made very limited sounds since I can not pay the subscription. but that's not the case, the fact is that I've been in music for about three years and I'll retire and I did not want to leave without giving help to the new ones (the project does not have Drums only the melodies and chords). (thanks for your attention)
The project: https://app.auxy.co/projects/UnzXJQbQAlhDf6jWWeQufg==
